urrence of a false\npositive signal in our first observation. Deeper observations are required to\nconfirm this hint of 150 MHz radio emission from HAT-P-11b.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2013 14:03:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
